      <p class="text-base text-gray-200">Online, invalid words are simply <span class="text-white font-medium">rejected with no penalty</span> — encouraging exploratory plays. On the board, challenges carry risk: if you challenge a valid word, <span class="text-white font-medium">you lose your turn</span>. This makes board Scrabble more psychologically complex.</p>
    </div>

