    </div>

    <p>The good news is that the most important skills — vocabulary depth and strategic thinking — transfer perfectly between formats. The format-specific skills (clock handling, reading body language) can be developed in parallel once you have the core word knowledge.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Online Etiquette & Fair Play</h2>

